cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NE

The paper deals with remote sensing data analysis using deep learning and distributed computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of modern computing hardware and resource optimization, which suggests the possibility of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) categories. The use of deep learning and machine learning techniques indicates the possibility of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) categories.
